{"tid":1703713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"救手足 ！！！","createTime":"2019-11-10T11:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T12:17:20.000Z","uid":227472,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"917f1ff26d280974d449e0f0d41f5c010acb141a","tid":1703713,"uid":227472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:43:33.000Z","msg":"今日又一城又有人俾狗拉左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小妹借人account出post 有少少野想要講 歡迎各位手足補充<br />\n見到有手足被人拉可以點？<br />\n1.一d人拎雜物（e.g.垃圾筒）擲狗分散佢哋注意力（遠攻）<br />\n2.搞唔掂嘅話我地人多 上前打狗（近攻）高危動作 pls掩護手足<br />\n3.哨兵 搵人幫拖<br />\n每次救手足都集氣勁耐 我哋人多過狗 唔好怯 怯就輸一世  成班人同3條粉皮吵都冇用 救手足至重要 <br />\n班狗仲驚過你 拎住支棍 咁細支防狼噴霧 呃OT wtf sorry for 1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79be7bd02047282980de5121bfe74923a1bf291","tid":1703713,"uid":227472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ae379b007058494e1bc9e10eb173c1aae68a180","tid":1703713,"uid":164059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"b11b73aadb99cffcf4f0f5480e5878f6395844fd","tid":1703713,"uid":38383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"室內戰好多記者圍人鍊 好難入同走"},{"pid":"b532a305e9f9503c271eb479b6df34f444eb9f3a","tid":1703713,"uid":262248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"用垃圾桶近戰好似好啲？<br />\n又可以防禦埋"},{"pid":"3d3e403ad382b12d21b22f667ac2509a9b19c789","tid":1703713,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T11:55:57.000Z","msg":"借分享 反送中運動警方行動紀錄<br />\n非編著人員<br />\n如版權被侵犯請通知<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline%2F&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6d409d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline/</a>"},{"pid":"2043004769cb193